Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.19,0:06:19.69,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx0\pos(15,20)\t(0,200,1,\fscx100)\t(5300,0,1,\fscx0)}———
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:19.52,neta3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,50,0,200)\pos(15,50)\fad(300,300)}（架空）在九州地区和日本各地的JAXA相关设施或活动上销售的薄荷味糖果，\N宣传广告语为“把宇宙的清爽送到您身边”，生产商为总部位于西之表市的“宇宙糖股份有限公司”。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.69,0:06:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糖…宇宙糖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有是有 只能给你一个哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.95,0:06:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.24,0:06:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.92,0:06:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要获胜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝方 中央种子岛高中 机器人研究部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,种岛机器3号改
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红方 前川静津也
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.52,0:06:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Devil Stronger
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.69,0:07:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于有上届进入决胜局淘汰赛的机体出场了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ROBO-ONE没有级别划分吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人也曾这么说过
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.24,0:07:18.54,Default-RR,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\p1\fscx200\fscy200\pos(88,662)} m 0 0 l -7 15 l -5 15 l -1 5 l 0 5
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:18.54,Default-R,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「就让我来告诉你 机体性能的差距决非战力的决定性差距吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 你那小男友的操纵水平比我高吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.55,0:07:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哥 看来你被操纵的不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.18,0:07:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,床上的操纵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 小秋你退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比试开始前叽叽喳喳说个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也算是败犬的典型特征了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.86,0:07:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是字面的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.98,0:07:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装模作样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我怎么击溃你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.24,0:07:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海 击溃他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打垮他！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.54,0:07:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正义必胜！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.41,0:07:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ready Fight！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜哇 好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 轻松搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNVAEL UPPER
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.93,0:08:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 Devil Stronger被击倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.02,0:08:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.85,0:08:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小秋 能不能别把招式名叫出来？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？ 必杀技就是用来叫的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新手运吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太得寸进尺了 小鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔！这么快就出现了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,0:08:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Devil Stronger的Double Lariat From Hell！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.59,0:08:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海！对方开始乱来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.76,0:08:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题 上半身旋转的那么厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.26,0:08:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就意味着下半身会非常不稳定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:08:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.94,0:09:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Devil Stronger出人意料的战斗不能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,种岛机器3改 一匹了不起的黑马出现！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.71,0:09:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大赛的新Hero诞生！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那动作还真是让人饶有兴趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.47,0:09:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中央种子岛高校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.14,0:09:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你的母校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.27,0:09:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在不知不觉间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们非常顺利地通过了预选
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决胜局淘汰赛阶段也无事胜出
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.45,0:09:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就只有决赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.91,0:09:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导入KILLBALA系统的操作系统
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.08,0:10:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和小秋是曾经在ROBO-ONE中获胜的美纱姐的妹妹这些事实
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都成为了话题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.38,0:10:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过总感觉像在做梦一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说出绝对要获胜的可是小秋你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是那么说啦
